    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "中军",
        "戚继光",
        "莫怀古",
        "莫文豪",
        "门子甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四刽子手、四龙套、四大铠、中军、二门子、莫文豪、戚继光同上。莫文豪升帐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蓟州总镇戚继光，参见老大人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贵镇卸了盔甲，再来讲话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢老大人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹牌子〗。戚继光换袍纱帽、捧册子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见大人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "门子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起，免，打恭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四刽子手、四龙套、四大铠同喊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谨将公文花名清册呈上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贵镇免礼。请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且问你：这蓟州目仓库如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仓库充满。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵丁将士？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵丁强壮，将士威严。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "营中器械？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀枪明亮，盔甲鲜明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "城中街道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四门齐整，街巷清尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！本院只望要报父仇，寻他的短处。怎奈他为官清廉，办事谨慎，这便怎\n处？好不闷坏吾也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "杀父之仇不能报，\n怎不叫人心內焦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫文豪吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中军老爷请过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人得的是何病症？"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕是途中受了风寒，得了伤风病症。"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此待我取杯茶来与大人所用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你快去取来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（戚继光取茶递中军，中军递莫文豪，莫文豪饮。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一霎时气得我昏迷不醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫文豪看杯。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见此杯想起了居家满门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，将戚继光与我绑了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人为何将我绑起来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且问你：这支杯子本是我家之物，你是哪里来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人若要问这杯子，却有杯主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这杯主是哪一个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是钱塘的莫怀古。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他如今还在么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么不在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在卑镇的衙中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你快快请他前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀大人呐！似这样绳捆索绑，是怎样去唤他呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中军，与他松绑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（戚继光下堂叫。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫仁兄快来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫怀古上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟你也来同吃一杯呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你还吃的是什么酒？大人叫我前来唤你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃是有罪之人，如何能去见他呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仁兄有所不知：适才大人到此，忽然得下风寒之症。弟因他是朝廷钦差，不敢\n怠慢。因将仁兄传家之宝与他看了一杯香茶。大人用下，病体果愈。不料他看\n见了杯子，就将小弟绑起。他说杯子是他家之物，追问此杯从何得的？我一时\n无奈，可就把你给端出来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，这便怎样呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人唤你，你要快快前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是怎能见他呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你快去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫文豪下座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀爹爹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿文豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿是文豪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫怀古、莫文豪同哭。〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是老贤侄到了。\n哈哈哈哈！你好吓！初次相逢，你就劲捆了我一绳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你得罪叔父，还不上前去赔罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知叔父在此，多有冒犯，望乞恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤侄吓！不要陪罪。只是少绑我一绳就够了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟：有道是不知者，不降罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古、莫文豪",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，你这一身荣耀，是哪里来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急三枪〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾儿既然作了八府巡按，就该上殿，参奏严贼才是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后堂排宴，一同畅饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恼恨严贼太狠心，"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一家骨肉两离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫文豪",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今朝父子重相见，"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫仁兄！"
        },
        {
          "character": "戚继光",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相逢仍在蓟州城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫怀古",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个“相逢仍在蓟州城”。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（莫怀古、戚继光、莫文豪同笑，同下。）"
        }
      ],
